00:11:58.988 --> 00:11:59.428
Father,

00:12:02.428 --> 00:12:05.667
I'm now the Emperor's trusted immortal.

00:12:06.228 --> 00:12:07.588
We can use this

00:12:09.428 --> 00:12:11.108
to save our family.

00:12:21.348 --> 00:12:23.348
(I'm the former Crown Prince.)

