(I'm)

00:12:26.747 --> 00:12:28.588
(the Young Master
that Feng Zuoren mentioned.)

00:12:35.292 --> 00:12:38.011
(Xue Family Ancestral Shrine)

00:12:47.611 --> 00:12:52.744
(Hexu, Seventh Generation)

00:12:54.068 --> 00:12:55.147
I'm Xue Hexu,

00:12:55.828 --> 00:12:56.627
